import React from 'react'; import './ExamSchedule.css'; function ExamSchedule() { return (

Examination Schedule

Course Date Time Mode Address/Link
Web Development 14th Dec 2024 10:00 AM to 12:00 PM Online Join Exam
AI & ML 15th Dec 2024 10:00 AM to 12:00 PM Offline UPES Bidholi
Data Science 15th Dec 2024 10:00 AM to 12:00 PM Offline UPES Bidholi

Examination Instructions

Offline Examination (AI & ML, Data Science)

  • Arrive at least 30 minutes before the scheduled exam time.
  • Bring your UPES ID card for verification.
  • Ensure to follow all safety protocols, including wearing a mask and maintaining social distance.
  • Only authorized materials are allowed in the exam hall. Personal items should be left in designated areas.

Online Examination (Web Development)

  • Ensure a stable internet connection for the duration of the exam.
  • Use a laptop or desktop for the best experience. Avoid mobile devices.
  • Log in at least 15 minutes before the exam starts to check your setup.
  • Keep your camera and microphone on throughout the exam. No external assistance is allowed.
); } export default ExamSchedule;
